### Working with Multiple Providers

Switch between different AI providers:

```bash
You: /provider openai
‚úÖ Switched to provider: openai

You: /model gpt-4o
‚úÖ Switched to model: gpt-4o

You: Write a Python function to sort a list
AI: Here's a Python function...

